      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST A MENACE (2) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 29.91 when a 0.8 lengths winner over 520m at this track last time. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Great chance again. SHADOW REAPER (6) collided in the run and missed the frame but ran fast time regardless when a 2.25 lengths fifth (42.48) in a Grade 5 at this track. Gets chance to atone. WEST ON JADE (4) struggled in tougher grade last start after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won by 3 lengths at this track (35.31) beating Queen Goddess in a Novice race on June 27. Has ability and can measure up. SAND FIRE (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
